    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention. The engine exhibits a consistent, heavy knocking sound, and the transmission struggles to engage properly, often slipping during acceleration. There are also visible signs of wear and tear on the body and interior, including some rust spots and upholstery damage. This car is ideal for a mechanic looking for a project or for someone needing a donor vehicle for parts. It is sold strictly as-is, and I recommend towing it rather than driving it away.",
