    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. Boasting a showroom-quality finish and an interior that remains in pristine, original condition, this motorcar represents the pinnacle of its class. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the expectations of the most discerning collector. Experience an automotive investment that combines timeless engineering with an aesthetic that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48900.0,
