    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person! I have babied this car since day one, and it is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and it drives like an absolute dream. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
