    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This example boasts a comprehensive service history, including a documented VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement already completed. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the variable M differential, ensuring optimal lateral grip and torque distribution. The suspension remains factory-spec with fresh bushings, maintaining the sharp turn-in and communicative feedback inherent to this platform. Finished in a concours-ready exterior with zero oxidation, this is a mechanically sorted, turn-key masterpiece for the purist collector.",
